tip.text: Amazing sushi, really loved their fresh salmon, both nigiri and hero roll. The shrimp crunchy roll was good too.
Amazing burgers and friendly service. I tried the steakhouse burger and it was 👍
Really fresh seafood. I really recommend their grilled seabass and grilled calamari. PS: they have playground if you have any kids.
Ordered tuna Tataki salad (amazing, raw tuna), beets and lentils (not bad), grilled shrimps with coconut rice (great). I loved the atmosphere and would come back.
Really liked the small mussels appetizer. The paella was good but too salty for my taste.
Tried okra fries, masala prawns, spicy lamb chops, chicken ruby and chicken berry britannia (biryani chicken). Highly recommend okra fries, chicken ruby and biryani chicken 😋
Lamb shoulder is a MUST.
Just discovered my new favorite burger joint in Dubai. Food is amazing, tried solar gravity burger and I loved it 😋
Eggplant fatta is great, mafrooka (dessert) is also good.
Went for quick sushi, volcano is a MUST (warm roll with scallops), crazy maki (it was ok) and salmon sushi (it was good 😋)

tip.text: Tried Urfa kebab and ribs "kuzu pirzola pors" and they are both amazing 😋
The salmon appetizer is good, don't forget to save some space for fried ice cream 😋
Pasadena burger is good, their fries is less than expected.
The luigia pizza with buffalo and truffles is a must. You can request it without ham but keep the bresaola (beef) 👌 don't miss the chiacchere Nutella desert 😋
If you like chocolate, their chocolate canya is from heaven 👌
My first ceviche,I tried seafood orgy ceviche and I really enjoyed it. Grilled octopus appetizer is a must.
Nocciolotto is simply amazing.
